exquisite accuracy of Scripture. Jesus stopped at, "The acceptable year
of the Lord," which is connected with the first advent and the
dispensation of grace, ([Gen 3:15](../../../bib/kjv/gen003.htm#015).md);

(See Scofield) - ([Act 1:11](../../../bib/kjv/act001.htm#011).md),

